snippet.title: DashShootGoal Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Dash Shoot Goal is a fast paced local multiplayer ball game for 1 to 4 players. Get it now on Itch.io:
https://catalyse.itch.io/dashshootgoal

Follow us on https://twitter.com/catalysestd
http://catalyse-studio.com/

Thanks to NCS for their sounds: Alive by Itro & Kontinuum
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-xKKo7t72Tg
https://soundcloud.com/itro
https://soundcloud.com/kontinuum
